des:
Get information about Los Angeles International Airport. 

Enable the skill and say "Alexa, start L.A.X." to begin. 

Get information on airlines location:
"Alexa, ask l. a. x. where is Delta Airlines located"

Get information on airlines by Terminals:
"Alexa, ask l. a. x. about Terminal 1"

Stay tuned as we add more features.
